reviewText:
A very good movie in this genre.  The reproduction of this copy could have been better.  Altogether it is worth the price.
  The women are fantastic, the acting is great.

Perfectly fine DVD for me! Compliments my SIGNED VHS copy quite well. Signed by Chrissy Mountjoy. Nice to have a simple, very good quality DVD to watch occasionally. I was really hunting this one. Satisfied customer!
The Spell Wears Off After a While
This DVD arrived in good shape and on time, but it would not play. This was a defective DVD. I was not able to watch it.
The movie was filmed in and around Melissa Wolf's home, but the lighting was dark on every "dream" sequence making it hard to see.  Those are over half the movie.
If you are a fan of Glorianne or Melissa, this is a must own. They are easy on the eyes. Fun movie, lots of nudity.
